<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="board-n">board <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /bɔːd/    美 /bɔːrd/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-c">1.★ <strong>[C] 板；木板；[用于构成合成词] …用木板：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a noticeboard
布告牌</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a diving board 
跳水板</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c-bre">2.★ <strong>[C] (BrE) 理事会；董事会；委员会；部：局：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>a board of directors
董事会</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>the Town Planning Board
城市规划委员会</p></div>

<h4 id="3u">3.<strong>[U] 伙食；膳食：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>When his family fell on hard times, he was offered free <strong>room and board</strong>.
艰难的时候他家里接济不上，有人给他提供了免费食宿。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="on-board">on board</h3>
<p>1.<strong>在船 / 火车 / 飞机上 (aboard)：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>On board the ship, you will be well taken care of. 
你在船上会受到很好的照顾。</p><footer>2008 全国</footer></div></div>